# ─── Google Sheets (required for sheet push) ──────────────────────────────────
# 1. console.cloud.google.com → New project → Enable "Google Sheets API" + "Google Drive API"
# 2. IAM → Service Accounts → Create → download JSON key → save as credentials.json
# 3. Share your Google Sheet with the service account email address
# 4. Copy the sheet ID from the URL: docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/<ID>/edit
SPREADSHEET_ID=your_spreadsheet_id_here
GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_FILE=credentials.json

# ─── Zillow via RapidAPI (optional — improves ARV accuracy with Zestimates) ───
# Free tier: rapidapi.com → search "Zillow Com1" → subscribe
# Without this the scanner still works using Redfin + HUD data only.
RAPIDAPI_KEY=

# ─── Tracker DB path (optional, defaults to deals.db in project folder) ───────
# TRACKER_DB=deals.db
